  "description": "Reverse mode engaged with negative speed — each grain plays a brief excerpt in reverse. posScatter at 0.55 means every grain starts at a different position, so the reversal is non-repeating. Mod wheel sweeps grain size from small (0.05, micro-reverse stutters) to large (0.6, full reversed phrases). The result sounds like time collapsing: you can hear something was said, but not what. Velocity controls the spread — soft = narrow, hard = the source fully randomized.",
